=1> Greetings Rangers!<br>
<br>
I am Merkur, and I have a question for the one's who visit here.  In my guild, there is a ranger who has always put others needs before his time and time again, always bending over backwards for us, giving his time to help us complete quests and take down mobs.<br>
<br>
Well, its time to pay him back.  We have helped him to get outfited in some thrug, but I belive that this is not enough for the help that he has shown us.  I want to try and find a better upgrade for his bow.  He is currently using Raincaller as the bow.  I am trying to find a logical upgrade for the bow, but as of yet, am unsure of what the step-up might be.<br>
<br>
I know he talked about having a decent bow with stats on it, I'm just lost to find somthing good for him.  I thought that I would come to this communtiy to try and anwser my querry.<br>
<br>
As a guild, we would be able to scrounge up:<br>
<br>
61 War<br>
60 Pally<br>
54 Pally<br>
54 Rogue<br>
60 Enchanter<br>
60 Cleric-epic<br>
57 Cleric<br>
52 Ranger<br>
52 Druid<br>
54 Wizzy-epic<br>
58 Wizzy<br>
57 Mage<br>
<br>
And lots between 50-40.<br>
<br>
Any advice on somthing we could be able to do together as a guild?  <br>
<br>
Thank you for you time<br>
<br>
