<br>
As for the Bow of the Huntsman, it is nice, definitely an upgrade from Raincaller, and does not have to be quested.  Gleed the Huntsman in the bank area of Kael drops it when killed.  I'm 99% certain it's an every time drop.<br>
<br>
Otherwise, if you have the cash, the BFT is very nice; check out the Fletching thread in this forum for information.  I think Alinor is doing combines on them, but be aware they have a high failure rate, even at max skill with Geerlok.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :\ --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/ohwell.gif ALT=":\"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
